Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小涼宮春日的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:52.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：NT000A；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}（4月1日  愚人節）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃綠先生癟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將我的遺骸灑向大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  把氣球丟到海裡會造成環境污染
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是長門同學  完全無視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以現在的演技是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之能吹氣讓我復原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黃綠先生為了救我而被壓在冰箱下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請將我的遺骸火化  骨灰灑向世界的中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  氣球是不能燒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我們看起來就像笨蛋一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  讓我出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是哪里卡住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…長門同學  黃綠先生好像出不來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  拉得太用力的話黃綠先生會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃綠先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我想要騙長門同學的話就不會這樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是我的錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  不要這麼責怪自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（整人）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:48.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小朝倉最終也沒能成功）

